Megatron:




Megatron ducked his head at the firepower and growled. "Yes, go. The sooner 
the better. I want you two to go to the flank of the ship and wait for an 
entrace. After the shields are deactivated Wildfire, Stingtra and I will 
take force to the inside through the ramp." He said to the other: "Now, to 
the front of the ship!" He took flight, towards the ship.

Quickstrike followed Dark Mouse.
